HEADWORD: Boistous
<hw>Bois"tous</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Rough or rude;
coarse; strong; violent; boisterous; noisy.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
<au>Chaucer.</au> -- <wordforms><wf>Bois"tous*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos>
-- <wf>Bois"tous*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark></wordforms> <au>Chaucer.</au>⟦br⟧
